{"tid":915362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話台灣仲有得選果啲，等你經濟命脈去晒中共手，我睇你仲選乜撚","createTime":"2018-11-25T02:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T04:44:07.000Z","uid":57376,"like":76,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ee43f47a38476a671a6f49246411a72976efdf","tid":915362,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:31:54.000Z","msg":"黎緊高雄經濟一定起飛架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中共就係要用高雄黎做示範<br />\n等其他垃圾窮縣睇到流晒口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n國民黨都一定大力放寬新移民＆中資進場<br />\n等你班台灣後生仔個個幫中資打工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等你地身邊每五個就有一個「新台灣人」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都享受到經濟成果之後仲敢反共？<br />\n邊個搵到錢之後會想窮？<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話民進黨做得好，但國民黨明顯係糖衣毒藥你都狗衝，仲要明知習種野心大到咁都要用台灣民主前途去搏一搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我終於知道你班台狗唔止係蠢，仲要係盲架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a4d01940cbc1f25344dbb5b0e1b00dcc574ba4","tid":915362,"uid":57376,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:45:06.000Z","msg":"做乜班人唔敢入黎反駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce7956d4f71858af1d7c561368e64c138f17e52","tid":915362,"uid":57376,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:47:30.000Z","msg":"入黎講下台灣點樣一邊賺大陸錢維生、一邊阻止畀中共統戰啦，阿叔好想學下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf9abe498e4ef329287a14ec7738436d106fe92","tid":915362,"uid":85659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:48:01.000Z","msg":"睇住d 覺青台狗 fb呢1年突然狂屌花媽。。。。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜選中。。。真係估0到咩回事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388758e8192a529501dbf7feef4e7dea9a8cc063","tid":915362,"uid":171192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:49:27.000Z","msg":"召喚李嘉欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b71c40997512d3116dd73624066a6bfbba54435","tid":915362,"uid":57376,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:51:13.000Z","msg":"香港又有五毛<br />\n台灣都有五毛<br />\n但至少連登仔寧願焦土捱杯麵都一定企硬不投共先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而有自主權嘅台狗就為咗冥幣狗衝，咁就唔好怪五毛洗腦啦<br />\n<br />\n除非台狗個腦部構造特啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9985af493fbc77cd0b8d7a35ac120a2e24c18be","tid":915362,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e1ee43f47a38476a671a6f49246411a72976efdf","tid":915362,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:31:54.000Z","msg":"黎緊高雄經濟一定起飛架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中共就係要用高雄黎做示範<br />\n等其他垃圾窮縣睇到流晒口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n國民黨都一定大力放寬新移民＆中資進場<br />\n等你班台灣後生仔個個幫中資打工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等你地身邊每五個就有一個「新台灣人」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都享受到經濟成果之後仲敢反共？<br />\n邊個搵到錢之後會想窮？<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話民進黨做得好，但國民黨明顯係糖衣毒藥你都狗衝，仲要明知習種野心大到咁都要用台灣民主前途去搏一搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我終於知道你班台狗唔止係蠢，仲要係盲架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:58:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6656/3288981\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6656%2F3288981&d=yVUO4YaWjgkNtiTYo0K70DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c4b09e1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6656/3288981</a><br />\n吳思瑤強調，總統蔡英文上任以來，就努力照顧所有在台新住民生活所需，包括開放陸配在公家機關工作限制、開放陸配前婚姻子女在台生活、就學便利等，也積極研擬放寬陸配報考各類技術考試限制、放寬陸配家屬來台探親資格限制等，都是希望陸配在台灣各項權益與生活能獲得更多保障與便利。<br />\n第一個咁做既咪蔡英文囉<br />\n阿叔,一隻手指對人幾多隻手指對番自己呀?<br />\n唔知頭唔知路就出黎柒呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20180803inv004/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.mg%2Fstory%2F20180803inv004%2F&d=yVUO4YaWjgkNtiTYo0K70DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=6d287616\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20180803inv004/</a><br />\n此外，吳思瑤表示，民進黨已成立新住民事務委員會，希望透過新住民委員參與，能直接聽取包含陸配在內的所有不同國籍新住民建議，作為與執政團隊溝通平台與政策擬定參考。吳表示，台灣是多元族群的社會，尊重多元族群亦是民進黨的基本理念。未來，民進黨將持續為在台灣之所有新住民，提供最好的生活照顧，讓每一個在台灣生活的人民都能安居樂業。<br />\n好好笑,打番晒自己把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f508326636bfd7f7c136a06089a0d30953a69ff","tid":915362,"uid":4713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"搵人貼比台仔睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31fcebdc2e94c3cf5047fd6882e20a08d8430ea2","tid":915362,"uid":57376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d9985af493fbc77cd0b8d7a35ac120a2e24c18be","tid":915362,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e1ee43f47a38476a671a6f49246411a72976efdf","tid":915362,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:31:54.000Z","msg":"黎緊高雄經濟一定起飛架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中共就係要用高雄黎做示範<br />\n等其他垃圾窮縣睇到流晒口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n國民黨都一定大力放寬新移民＆中資進場<br />\n等你班台灣後生仔個個幫中資打工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等你地身邊每五個就有一個「新台灣人」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都享受到經濟成果之後仲敢反共？<br />\n邊個搵到錢之後會想窮？<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話民進黨做得好，但國民黨明顯係糖衣毒藥你都狗衝，仲要明知習種野心大到咁都要用台灣民主前途去搏一搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我終於知道你班台狗唔止係蠢，仲要係盲架